                                he says that he had written;
                            le/gei o(/ti e)/grayen,
                                he says that he wrote;
                            le/gei o(/ti gra/yei, he says that he shall write.

*fhsi\ (fh/sei) gra/yein, he
                            says (or will say) that he will write;
